101114134628/http://www.temple.edu/architecture] [[Philadelphia|Philadelphia, Pennsylvania]]\n*[[Texas A&M University]], [[College Station, Texas]]\n*[[Texas Tech University]], [[Lubbock, Texas]]\n*[[Tulane School of Architecture|Tulane University]], [[New Orleans|New Orleans, Louisiana]]\n*[[University of Arizona]]*, College of Architecture and Landscape Architecture, [http://cala.arizona.edu/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=407&Itemid=203] [[Tucson, Arizona]]\n*[[University of California, Berkeley]], [[University of California, Berkeley College of Environmental Design|College of Environmental Design]], [http://arch.ced.berkeley.edu/] [[Berkeley, California|Berkeley]], [[California]]\n*[[University of California, Los Angeles]], Department of Architecture and Urban Design, [http://www.aud.ucla.edu/] [[Los Angeles|Los Angeles, California]]\n*[[University of Cincinnati]], [[University of Cincinnati College of Design, Architecture, Art, and Planning|College of Design, Architecture, Art and Planning]], [[Cincinnati|Cincinnati, Ohio]]\n*[[University of Colorado Denver]], [[Denver|Denver, Colorado]]\n*[[University of Detroit Mercy]], [[Detroit|Detroit, Michigan]]\n*[[University of Florida]], [[Gainesville, Florida]]\n*[[University of Hartford]], Department of Architecture, [[Hartford, Connecticut]]\n*[[University of Houston]], [[Hines College of Architecture|Gerald D. Hines College of Architecture]]*, [[Houston|Houston, Texas]]\n*[[University of Idaho]], [[Moscow, Idaho]]\n*[[University of Illinois at Chicago]]*, [[Chicago|Chicago, Illinois]]\n*[[University of Illinois at Urbana\u2013Champaign]]\n*[[University of Kansas]], School of Architecture, Design, and Planning, [http://www.sadp.ku.edu] [[Lawrence, Kansas|Lawrence]], [[Kansas]] *\n*[[University of Kentucky]], College of Design, [https://web.archive.org/web/20070326123407/http://www.uky.edu/Design/architecturedegrees.html] [[Lexington, Kentucky|Lexington]], [[Kentucky]] *\n*[[University of Louisiana at La